posts.post_title: FS: T206 Lena Blackburne PSA 7 HIGHEST GRADED - VERY SHARP $650
posts.post_content:
Hello all -
I have a T206 Lena Blackburne PSA 7 for sale for $650 (paypal gift or the equivalent).  This card is incredibly sharp - with a touch to the top and bottom right corners preventing an 8.  My scanner isn't so sharp with graded cards - but a beautiful perfectly solid 7.  

According to PSA's Population Report there are 10 7's and 4 8's total for Blackburne - with this being the only graded 7 and highest 'T206 Sweet Caporal' example.  Definitely a tough high grade common.
